{
  "video_id": "WMahpWvAPWo",
  "title": "A civil response to violence (with English subtitles) | Emiliano Salinas",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Carolina Montero Reviewer: Sebastian Betti"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15960.0,
      "end_time": 17460.0,
      "text": "My name is Emiliano Salinas"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17460.0,
      "end_time": 21660.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to talk about the role"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21660.0,
      "end_time": 23760.0,
      "text": "we members of society play"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23760.0,
      "end_time": 25600.0,
      "text": "in the violent atmosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25600.0,
      "end_time": 28390.0,
      "text": "this country is living in right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28400.0,
      "end_time": 31459.0,
      "text": "I was born in 1976."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31460.0,
      "end_time": 34860.0,
      "text": "I grew up in a traditional Mexican family."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34860.0,
      "end_time": 36860.0,
      "text": "As a child, I had a pretty normal life:"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36860.0,
      "end_time": 40960.0,
      "text": "I would go to school, play with my friends and cousins."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40960.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "But then my father became President of Mexico"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 46760.0,
      "text": "and my life changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46760.0,
      "end_time": 49590.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m about to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49600.0,
      "end_time": 50560.0,
      "text": "at least some of what I&#39;m about to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50560.0,
      "end_time": 52360.0,
      "text": "will cause controversy."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52360.0,
      "end_time": 55460.0,
      "text": "Firstly, because I&#39;m the one who&#39;s going to say it."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55460.0,
      "end_time": 58460.0,
      "text": "And secondly, because what I&#39;m going to say is true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58460.0,
      "end_time": 60460.0,
      "text": "and it will make a lot of people nervous"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60460.0,
      "end_time": 63110.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s something we don&#39;t want to hear."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63110.0,
      "end_time": 65160.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s imperative that we listen"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65160.0,
      "end_time": 67518.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s undeniable and definitive."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67518.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "It will also make members of"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 71195.0,
      "text": "criminal organizations nervous"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71195.0,
      "end_time": 72960.0,
      "text": "for the same reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72960.0,
      "end_time": 76160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk about the role"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76160.0,
      "end_time": 77997.0,
      "text": "we members of society play"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77998.0,
      "end_time": 79560.0,
      "text": "in this phenomenon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79560.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "and about four different response levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 85560.0,
      "text": "we citizens have against violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85560.0,
      "end_time": 87760.0,
      "text": "I know many will find it difficult to separate the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87760.0,
      "end_time": 89660.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m Carlos Salinas de Gortari&#39;s son"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89660.0,
      "end_time": 91460.0,
      "text": "from the fact that I&#39;m a citizen"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91460.0,
      "end_time": 93259.0,
      "text": "concerned about the country&#39;s current situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 94460.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t worry."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 94460.0,
      "end_time": 96460.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not necessary for understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96460.0,
      "end_time": 99960.0,
      "text": "the importance of what I&#39;m going to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 99960.0,
      "end_time": 101660.0,
      "text": "I think we have a problem in Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101660.0,
      "end_time": 102960.0,
      "text": "We have a big problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 102960.0,
      "end_time": 104960.0,
      "text": "I think there&#39;s consensus on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104960.0,
      "end_time": 105960.0,
      "text": "No one argues --"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 105960.0,
      "end_time": 107259.0,
      "text": "we all agree there&#39;s a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 108760.0,
      "text": "What we don&#39;t agree on"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 108760.0,
      "end_time": 112600.0,
      "text": "is what the problem actually is."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 112600.0,
      "end_time": 116760.0,
      "text": "Is it the Zetas? The drug traffickers? The government?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 116760.0,
      "end_time": 120960.0,
      "text": "Corruption? Poverty? Or is it something else?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 120960.0,
      "end_time": 123160.0,
      "text": "I think none of these is the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123160.0,
      "end_time": 125460.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t mean they don&#39;t deserve attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 125460.0,
      "end_time": 127929.0,
      "text": "But we won&#39;t be able to take care of any of those things"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 127930.0,
      "end_time": 130600.0,
      "text": "if we don&#39;t solve the real problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130600.0,
      "end_time": 131560.0,
      "text": "we have in Mexico first."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 131560.0,
      "end_time": 132950.0,
      "text": "The real problem we have is"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 132950.0,
      "end_time": 136160.0,
      "text": "most of us Mexicans, we believe we are victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 136160.0,
      "end_time": 137906.0,
      "text": "of our circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 137906.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "We are a country of victims."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 143100.0,
      "text": "Historically, we&#39;ve always acted as victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 143100.0,
      "end_time": 144780.0,
      "text": "of something or somebody."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 144780.0,
      "end_time": 147600.0,
      "text": "We were victims of the Spaniards."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 147600.0,
      "end_time": 149800.0,
      "text": "Then we were victims of the French."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 149800.0,
      "end_time": 151524.0,
      "text": "Then we were victims of Don Porfirio."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 151524.0,
      "end_time": 153676.0,
      "text": "Then we were victims of the PRI."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 153676.0,
      "end_time": 155359.0,
      "text": "Even of Salinas."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 155360.0,
      "end_time": 157481.0,
      "text": "And of El Peje."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 157481.0,
      "end_time": 160466.0,
      "text": "And now of the Zetas and the traffickers and the criminals and the kidnappers ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 160467.0,
      "end_time": 162947.0,
      "text": "Hold on! Wait a minute!"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 162947.0,
      "end_time": 166482.0,
      "text": "What if none of these things is the problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 166482.0,
      "end_time": 169785.0,
      "text": "The problem is not the things we feel victims of."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 169785.0,
      "end_time": 173984.0,
      "text": "The problem is that we play the role of victims."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 173985.0,
      "end_time": 177760.0,
      "text": "We need to open our eyes and see that we are not victims."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 177760.0,
      "end_time": 179959.0,
      "text": "If only we stopped feeling like victims,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 179960.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "if we stopped acting as victims,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 184482.0,
      "text": "our country would change so much!"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 184495.0,
      "end_time": 187960.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk about how to go from a society"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 187960.0,
      "end_time": 189659.0,
      "text": "that acts as a victim of circumstances"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 189659.0,
      "end_time": 192560.0,
      "text": "to a responsible, involved society"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 192560.0,
      "end_time": 196960.0,
      "text": "that takes the future of its country in its own hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196960.0,
      "end_time": 198560.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk about four different levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198560.0,
      "end_time": 200660.0,
      "text": "of civil response against violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 200660.0,
      "end_time": 202960.0,
      "text": "from weakest"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 202960.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "to strongest."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207760.0,
      "text": "The first level, the weakest level of civil response against violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 207760.0,
      "end_time": 210660.0,
      "text": "is denial and apathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 210660.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "Today, much of Mexican society is in denial"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "of the situation we&#39;re going through."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218518.0,
      "text": "We want to go on with our daily life"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 218518.0,
      "end_time": 221600.0,
      "text": "even though we are not living under normal circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 221600.0,
      "end_time": 223760.0,
      "text": "Daily life in our country is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 223760.0,
      "end_time": 226989.0,
      "text": "to say the least,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 226989.0,
      "end_time": 228953.0,
      "text": "under extraordinary, exceptional circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 228953.0,
      "end_time": 232760.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like someone who has a serious illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 232760.0,
      "end_time": 234760.0,
      "text": "and pretends it&#39;s the flu"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 234760.0,
      "end_time": 236730.0,
      "text": "and it will just go away."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 236730.0,
      "end_time": 239971.0,
      "text": "We want to pretend that Mexico has the flu."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 239971.0,
      "end_time": 242730.0,
      "text": "But it doesn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 242730.0,
      "end_time": 244290.0,
      "text": "Mexico has cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 244290.0,
      "end_time": 246459.0,
      "text": "And if we don&#39;t do something about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 246460.0,
      "end_time": 249614.0,
      "text": "the cancer will end up killing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 249614.0,
      "end_time": 252600.0,
      "text": "We need to move Mexican society"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 252600.0,
      "end_time": 254600.0,
      "text": "from denial and apathy"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 254600.0,
      "end_time": 256459.0,
      "text": "to the next level of citizen response,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 256459.0,
      "end_time": 259591.0,
      "text": "which is, effectively, recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 259591.0,
      "end_time": 263426.0,
      "text": "And that recognition will sow fear --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 263426.0,
      "end_time": 266585.0,
      "text": "recognizing the seriousness of the situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 266585.0,
      "end_time": 270232.0,
      "text": "But, fear is better than apathy"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 270232.0,
      "end_time": 273546.0,
      "text": "because fear makes us do something."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 273546.0,
      "end_time": 276789.0,
      "text": "Many people in Mexico"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 276789.0,
      "end_time": 278746.0,
      "text": "are afraid today."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 278746.0,
      "end_time": 280222.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re very afraid."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 280222.0,
      "end_time": 282359.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re acting out of that fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 282360.0,
      "end_time": 284600.0,
      "text": "And let me tell you what the problem is"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 284600.0,
      "end_time": 285760.0,
      "text": "with acting out of fear --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 285760.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "and this is the second level of civil response:"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 289860.0,
      "text": "fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 289860.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s think about Mexican streets:"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295760.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re unsafe because of violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 295760.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "so people stay at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 302460.0,
      "text": "Does that make streets more or less safe?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 302460.0,
      "end_time": 303460.0,
      "text": "Less safe!"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 303460.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "So streets become more desolate and unsafe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 306659.0,
      "text": "so we stay home more --"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 306660.0,
      "end_time": 309600.0,
      "text": "which makes streets even more desolate and unsafe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 309600.0,
      "end_time": 310560.0,
      "text": "and we stay home even more."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 310560.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "This vicious circle ends up with the whole population"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "stuck inside their houses, scared to death --"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317760.0,
      "text": "even more afraid than when we were out on the streets."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 317760.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "We need to confront this fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 322659.0,
      "text": "We need to move Mexican society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 322660.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "the members of society who are at this level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 327460.0,
      "text": "to the next level, which is action."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 327460.0,
      "end_time": 331460.0,
      "text": "We need to face our fears and take back our streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 331460.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "our cities, our neighborhoods."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 340460.0,
      "text": "For many people, acting involves courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 340460.0,
      "end_time": 342460.0,
      "text": "We go from fear to courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 342460.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "They say, \"I can&#39;t take it anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s do something about it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "Recently --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "this is a sensitive figure --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 356460.0,
      "text": "35 public lynchings have been recorded"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 356460.0,
      "end_time": 358600.0,
      "text": "so far in 2010"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 358600.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "in Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 365659.0,
      "text": "Usually it&#39;s one or two a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 365660.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;re experiencing one every week."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 368260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "This shows that society is desperate"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 374760.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s taking the law into its own hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 374760.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, violent action --"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "though action is better than no action --"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "but taking part in it"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 385760.0,
      "text": "only disguises violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 385760.0,
      "end_time": 388260.0,
      "text": "If I&#39;m violent with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "and you respond with violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "you become part of the violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "and you just disguise my violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398460.0,
      "text": "So civil action"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 398460.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "is vital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s also vital to take people"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 404460.0,
      "text": "who are at the level of courage"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 404460.0,
      "end_time": 406260.0,
      "text": "and violent action"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "to the next level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 409860.0,
      "text": "which is non-violent action."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 409860.0,
      "end_time": 412760.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s pacific, coordinated civil action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 412760.0,
      "end_time": 414760.0,
      "text": "which doesn&#39;t mean passive action."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 414760.0,
      "end_time": 417560.0,
      "text": "It means it&#39;s determined and effective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 417560.0,
      "end_time": 420600.0,
      "text": "but not violent."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 420600.0,
      "end_time": 422760.0,
      "text": "There are examples of this kind of action in Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 422760.0,
      "end_time": 427460.0,
      "text": "Two years ago, in Galena City, Chihuahua,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 427460.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "a member of the community was kidnapped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 430960.0,
      "text": "Eric Le Barón."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 430960.0,
      "end_time": 432560.0,
      "text": "His brothers, Benjamín and Julián,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 432560.0,
      "end_time": 434560.0,
      "text": "got together with the rest of the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 434560.0,
      "end_time": 436960.0,
      "text": "to think of the best course of action:"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 436960.0,
      "end_time": 439600.0,
      "text": "to pay the ransom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 439600.0,
      "end_time": 443560.0,
      "text": "to take up arms and go after the kidnappers"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 443560.0,
      "end_time": 445860.0,
      "text": "or to ask the government for help."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 445860.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "In the end, Benjamín and Julián decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "the best thing they could do"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 453600.0,
      "text": "was to organize the community and act together."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 453600.0,
      "end_time": 454760.0,
      "text": "So what did they do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 454760.0,
      "end_time": 457600.0,
      "text": "They mobilized the whole community of Le Barón"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 457600.0,
      "end_time": 459860.0,
      "text": "to go to Chihuahua,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 459860.0,
      "end_time": 462260.0,
      "text": "where they organized a sit-in"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 464560.0,
      "text": "in the central park of the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 464560.0,
      "end_time": 466460.0,
      "text": "They sent a message to the kidnappers:"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 466460.0,
      "end_time": 469460.0,
      "text": "\"If you want your ransom come and get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 469460.0,
      "end_time": 471859.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll be waiting for you right here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 471860.0,
      "end_time": 473860.0,
      "text": "They stayed there."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 473860.0,
      "end_time": 476360.0,
      "text": "Seven days later, Eric was set free"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 476360.0,
      "end_time": 478360.0,
      "text": "and was able to return home."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 478360.0,
      "end_time": 482160.0,
      "text": "This is an example of what an organized society can do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 482160.0,
      "end_time": 484760.0,
      "text": "a society that acts."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 484760.0,
      "end_time": 486960.0,
      "text": "Of course, criminals can respond."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 486960.0,
      "end_time": 488960.0,
      "text": "And in this case, they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 488960.0,
      "end_time": 492260.0,
      "text": "On July 7th, 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 492260.0,
      "end_time": 494760.0,
      "text": "Benjamín Le Barón was murdered."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 494760.0,
      "end_time": 497460.0,
      "text": "But Julián Le Barón keeps working"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 497460.0,
      "end_time": 499659.0,
      "text": "and he has been mobilizing communities in Chihuahua"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 499660.0,
      "end_time": 502260.0,
      "text": "for over a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 502260.0,
      "end_time": 504960.0,
      "text": "And for over a year he has known that a price has been put on his head."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 504960.0,
      "end_time": 506760.0,
      "text": "But he keeps fighting."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 506760.0,
      "end_time": 508260.0,
      "text": "He keeps organizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 508260.0,
      "end_time": 510260.0,
      "text": "He keeps mobilizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 510260.0,
      "end_time": 512860.0,
      "text": "These heroic acts are present all over the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 512860.0,
      "end_time": 515260.0,
      "text": "With a thousand Juliáns working together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "Mexico would be a very different country."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 518760.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re out there!"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 518760.0,
      "end_time": 523260.0,
      "text": "They just have to raise their hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 523260.0,
      "end_time": 529260.0,
      "text": "I was born in Mexico, I grew up in Mexico"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 529260.0,
      "end_time": 534260.0,
      "text": "and along the way, I learned to love Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 534260.0,
      "end_time": 537460.0,
      "text": "I think anyone who has stepped foot on this land --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 537460.0,
      "end_time": 539460.0,
      "text": "not to mention all Mexican people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 539460.0,
      "end_time": 542260.0,
      "text": "will agree that it&#39;s not difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 542260.0,
      "end_time": 545260.0,
      "text": "to love Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 545260.0,
      "end_time": 547760.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve traveled a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 547760.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "and nowhere else have I found the passion Mexicans have."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 553260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "That devotion we feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 557260.0,
      "text": "for the national football team."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 559260.0,
      "text": "That devotion we show"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 561260.0,
      "text": "in helping victims of disasters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 561260.0,
      "end_time": 563260.0,
      "text": "such as the earthquake in 1985"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 563260.0,
      "end_time": 565760.0,
      "text": "or this year&#39;s floods."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 565760.0,
      "end_time": 571260.0,
      "text": "The passion with which we&#39;ve been singing the national anthem"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 571260.0,
      "end_time": 572760.0,
      "text": "since we were kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 572760.0,
      "end_time": 574260.0,
      "text": "When we thought Masiosare"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 574260.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "was the strange enemy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 577260.0,
      "end_time": 579760.0,
      "text": "and we sang, with a childlike heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 579760.0,
      "end_time": 584960.0,
      "text": "\"a soldier in each son.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 584960.0,
      "end_time": 587260.0,
      "text": "I think the biggest insult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 589260.0,
      "text": "the worst way you can offend a Mexican"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 589260.0,
      "end_time": 591600.0,
      "text": "is to insult their mother."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 591600.0,
      "end_time": 595260.0,
      "text": "A mother is the most sacred thing in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 595260.0,
      "end_time": 598260.0,
      "text": "Mexico is our mother and today she cries out for her children."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 598260.0,
      "end_time": 601260.0,
      "text": "We are going through the darkest moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 601260.0,
      "end_time": 603260.0,
      "text": "in our recent history."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 603260.0,
      "end_time": 606960.0,
      "text": "Our mother, Mexico, is being violated before our very eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 606960.0,
      "end_time": 609960.0,
      "text": "What are we going to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 609960.0,
      "end_time": 612460.0,
      "text": "Masiosare, the strange enemy, is here."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 612460.0,
      "end_time": 617260.0,
      "text": "Where is the soldier in each son?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 617260.0,
      "end_time": 619260.0,
      "text": "Mahatma Gandhi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 619260.0,
      "end_time": 623600.0,
      "text": "one of the greatest civil fighters of all time, said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 623600.0,
      "end_time": 627600.0,
      "text": "\"Be the change you wish to see in the world.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 627600.0,
      "end_time": 630260.0,
      "text": "Today in Mexico we&#39;re asking for Gandhis."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 630260.0,
      "end_time": 632760.0,
      "text": "We need Gandhis."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 632760.0,
      "end_time": 635760.0,
      "text": "We need men and women who love Mexico"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 635760.0,
      "end_time": 638760.0,
      "text": "and who are willing to take action."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 638760.0,
      "end_time": 643760.0,
      "text": "This is a call for every true Mexican"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 643760.0,
      "end_time": 645760.0,
      "text": "to join this initiative."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 645760.0,
      "end_time": 647260.0,
      "text": "This is a call"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 647260.0,
      "end_time": 650260.0,
      "text": "so that every single thing we love about Mexico --"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 650260.0,
      "end_time": 652260.0,
      "text": "the festivals, the markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 652260.0,
      "end_time": 654260.0,
      "text": "the restaurants, the cantinas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 654260.0,
      "end_time": 657260.0,
      "text": "the tequila, the mariachis, the serenades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 657260.0,
      "end_time": 661600.0,
      "text": "the posadas, El Grito, the Day of the Dead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 661600.0,
      "end_time": 664459.0,
      "text": "San Miguel, the joy, the passion for life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 664460.0,
      "end_time": 668660.0,
      "text": "the fight and everything it means to be Mexican --"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 668660.0,
      "end_time": 673600.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t disappear from this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 673600.0,
      "end_time": 676260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re facing a very powerful opponent."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 676260.0,
      "end_time": 678760.0,
      "text": "But we are many more."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 678760.0,
      "end_time": 681260.0,
      "text": "They can take a man&#39;s life."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 681260.0,
      "end_time": 683260.0,
      "text": "Anyone can kill me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 683260.0,
      "end_time": 684760.0,
      "text": "or you, or you."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 684760.0,
      "end_time": 687260.0,
      "text": "But no one can kill"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 687260.0,
      "end_time": 689760.0,
      "text": "the spirit of true Mexicans."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 689760.0,
      "end_time": 691760.0,
      "text": "The battle is won,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 691760.0,
      "end_time": 694660.0,
      "text": "but we still have to fight it."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 694660.0,
      "end_time": 700260.0,
      "text": "2000 years ago, the Roman poet Juvenal"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 700260.0,
      "end_time": 703260.0,
      "text": "said something that today echoes"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 703260.0,
      "end_time": 706260.0,
      "text": "in the heart of every true Mexican."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 706260.0,
      "end_time": 710560.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Count it the greatest sin"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 710560.0,
      "end_time": 716260.0,
      "text": "to prefer life to honor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 716260.0,
      "end_time": 720260.0,
      "text": "and for the sake of living"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 720260.0,
      "end_time": 723860.0,
      "text": "to lose what makes life worth living.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 723860.0,
      "end_time": 725260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 725260.0,
      "end_time": 728260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}